FBIS4-65318 "drweu094_p_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-094 Daily Report 13 May 1994 GREECE Foreign Minister Says Albanian Gesture `Positive' Foreign Minister Says Albanian Gesture `Positive' NC1305165094 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1500 GMT 13 May 94 NC1305165094 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] After hearing of Albanian President Sali Berisha's statement yesterday on his willingness to visit Athens to defuse the recent crisis, Foreign Minister Karolos Papoulias described this change in stance as a positive gesture. Mr. Papoulias added: The meeting between the two sides must be prepared properly and we should proceed with practical measures, primarily with those that are open and concern the Greek minority.
